{
  "stem": "27335.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had other-- other papers, but that was the one my-- that-- that was-- I'm going to use to-- to-- to get-- get back-- back across.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they just smiled.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, because, they-- they knew the-- they knew the person.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, the tragedy?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so, they did-- they put me up in a military-- military barracks in the-- in a-- in a cell.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they put two armed guards on the-- and my-- my hands, they never took it off.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Behind my back, and there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I just slept like this, you see, or what I could.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the morning, they put me in a car with a Ukrainian in a-- in a Soviet uniform, a Ukrainian partisan they captured during the ride somewhere, operating.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Those were the real guys, [INAUDIBLE]. 1,000 kilometers ahead of Red Army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they dispersed into no-- no language, or nothing, but just [INAUDIBLE] and do something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Kill a fascist, or blow up something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anyway, we were the two-- two-- two-- two prisoners, and then an-- an officer-- an officer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think he was in the rank of captain, who was then an-- an-- a chauffeur.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we landed in-- landed in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In between time, things-- small things has happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In [NON-ENGLISH], that was the Northern-- Northern station up the Hungarian counterintelligence.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that was the nearest to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they-- they placed us in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they put me in cell number 1.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was the-- it was the isolated-- isolated cell.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Next morning, they-- they led me out to the-- to the-- to the gate, to the door, into the-- but it was a thick wall, and so I couldn't-- I couldn't see the firing squad.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I could see the-- that's how they placed me.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
